    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217060/extras/f495ad77eec5b9653ac936b3afd69b9f.poster.avif?t=1678395558\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217060/extras/f495ad77eec5b9653ac936b3afd69b9f.webm?t=1678395558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fusing the styles of Classic Point and Click Adventure with Side-Scrolling Shooter- Graceward creates a fresh experience, steeped in old school design. </strong><br><br>&quot;Buried in this dark future is something raw. A deep and primal energy that runs like blood under the ground. Is it a rebellion against our fates? A grasp at a second chance? Or is it just the heat of last night’s fires, still clung to the breeze for a short while longer...&quot; <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217060/extras/a02fc8555238151527fe87465e044d33.poster.avif?t=1678395558\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217060/extras/a02fc8555238151527fe87465e044d33.webm?t=1678395558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217060/extras/a02fc8555238151527fe87465e044d33.mp4?t=1678395558\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Featuring from the Shooter side of the family:</strong><br><br>• Hand-designed levels with dozens of hidden secrets, calling-back to 90s FPS's. <br><br>• A heavy original score full of industrial sound, heavy metal, and haunting melodies. <br><br>• And several hundred gallons of enemy blood.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217060/extras/ad031d454a0860a33cb3f388cb30eeba.poster.avif?t=1678395558\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217060/extras/ad031d454a0860a33cb3f388cb30eeba.webm?t=1678395558\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>And from the Adventure Game side:</strong><br><br>• Form relationships and choose which companions will accompany you.<br><br>• Learn skills to solve familiar and unfamiliar puzzles and mysteries.<br><br>• And make tough decisions which will twist and turn the narrative.",
